ents (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"ic_layers.svg":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.svg"}],"type":"image","identifier":"ic_layers.svg"},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"title":"the following guidelines","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}],"url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"}}}